<channel|>冇問題，我明白晒。我會用道地嘅廣東話同埋你要求嘅格式嚟完成呢個任務。

「睇怕」喺廣東話入面通常用嚟表示「推測」、「估計」或者「恐怕」，帶有一種根據現有情況去判斷未來可能會發生某事嘅意思。

以下係 10 句關於「睇怕」嘅例句：

# 詞: 睇怕

1. 睇怕聽日會落大雨，你出街記得帶遮。 (It looks like it's going to rain heavily tomorrow, remember to bring an umbrella when you go out.)
2. 佢咁樣行法，睇怕今次比賽好難贏到。 (Judging by the way he's playing, I'm afraid it'll be hard for him to win this competition.)
3. 睇怕佢今日唔會返嚟喇，佢話要去睇醫生。 (I reckon he won't be coming back today; he said he has to go see a doctor.)
4. 呢間餐廳排隊排得咁耐，睇怕要等好耐先食到。 (The queue at this restaurant is so long, I'm afraid we'll have to wait a long time to eat.)
5. 睇怕佢哋兩個好難會和好，因為大家都有啲倔強。 (It looks like the two of them will find it hard to make up, because both are quite stubborn.)
6. 佢咁樣唔做功課，睇怕考試嗰陣會好大鑊。 (If he keeps not doing his homework like this, I'm afraid he'll be in big trouble during the exam.)
7. 睇怕呢個計劃行唔通，因為預算太少喇。 (I suspect this plan won't work because the budget is too small.)
8. 佢成日遲到，睇怕老闆遲早會唔滿意。 (He's always late; I'm afraid the boss will eventually be dissatisfied.)
9. 睇怕今晚要加班喇，因為仲有好多嘢未搞掂。 (It looks like I'll have to work overtime tonight because there's still a lot of unfinished work.)
10. 佢咁樣講嘢，睇怕係想挑釁人哋。 (Judging by the way he's talking, I suspect he's trying to provoke others.) [end of text]


